    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make maternity pay full pay for 1 year.",
        "additional_details": "Lets encourage the government to male maternity pay full pay for 1 year regardless of what company you work for. The 1st year in a child\u2019s life is the most important and limiting our time with our children due to funds is an unwanted stress, we should be encouraged to start families not put us off and choose between work or time with our children for the first year. Offering SMP for the first year is just not enough, every pregnancy and birth is different many have complications which affect our ML.",
        "background": "Let\u2019s make maternity pay full for 1 year.\r\nSMP is 90% of your average weekly earnings (before tax) for the first 6 weeks\r\n\u00a3148.68 or 90% of your average weekly earnings (whichever is lower) for the next 33 weeks.",
